#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nanmean.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nanmean"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean:1 of
msgid "Compute the arithmetic mean along the specified axis, ignoring NaNs."
msgstr "沿指定轴计算算术平均值，忽略 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns the average of the tensor elements.  The average is taken over "
"the flattened tensor by default, otherwise over the specified axis. "
"`float64` intermediate and return values are used for integer inputs."
msgstr ""
"返回张量元素的平均值。默认情况下，平均值是在展平的张量上计算的，否则在"
"指定轴上计算。对于整数输入，使用 `float64` 类型作为中间和返回值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean:7 of
msgid "For all-NaN slices, NaN is returned and a `RuntimeWarning` is raised."
msgstr "对于全为 NaN 的切片，返回 NaN 并引发 `RuntimeWarning`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean:9 of
msgid ""
"Tensor containing numbers whose mean is desired. If `a` is not an tensor,"
" a conversion is attempted."
msgstr "包含要求平均值的数字的张量。如果 `a` 不是张量，则尝试进行转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean:12 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the means are computed. The default is to compute the "
"mean of the flattened tensor."
msgstr "计算平均值的轴。默认情况下计算展平张量的平均值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean:15 of
msgid ""
"Type to use in computing the mean.  For integer inputs, the default is "
"`float64`; for inexact inputs, it is the same as the input dtype."
msgstr ""
"用于计算平均值的类型。对于整数输入，默认为 `float64`；对于不精确输入，它"
"与输入的 dtype 相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean:19 of
msgid ""
"Alternate output tensor in which to place the result.  The default is "
"``None``; if provided, it must have the same shape as the expected "
"output, but the type will be cast if necessary.  See `doc.ufuncs` for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出张量。默认为 ``None``；如果提供，它必须具有与预期"
"输出相同的形状，但类型在必要时将被强制转换。有关详细信息，请参见 `doc."
"ufuncs`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanmean.nanmean:24 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result"
" as dimensions with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast"
" correctly against the original `a`.  If the value is anything but the "
"default, then `keepdims` will be passed through to the `mean` or `sum` "
"methods of sub-classes of `Tensor`.  If the sub-classes methods does not "
"implement `keepdims` any exceptions will be raised."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则被压缩的轴将保留在结果中作为大小为一的维度。使用此选项"
"，结果将能正确广播到原始 `a`。如果值不是默认值，则 `keepdims` 将传递给 `"
"Tensor` 子类的 `mean` 或 `sum` 方法。如果子类方法未实现 `keepdims`，将"
"引发异常。"

